ong> Measure from top of neck to bottom of seam.</p><p><strong>Arm length (D):</strong> measure from side of neck seam at base of collar, to knuckles.</p><p><strong>Bicep (E):</strong> Measure around thinnest part above bicep.</p><p><strong>Hand  (F): </strong>Measure around the knuckles of your four fingers.  (this garment has thumb hole so it covers front of hand.)</p>","button_text":"Button","link":"","center_align":false,"text_color":"#606060","background_color":"#f7f7f7"}},"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"page_width":100}}},"order":["richtext_editorial_columns_mnDFnG","richtext_custom_liquid_69rz68","image_with_text_3xhaPq","richtext_custom_liquid_PVexdK","image_with_text_gxMdWM","richtext_custom_liquid_4gga7B","image_with_text_CK6Ucy","richtext_custom_liquid_NqpqH7","image_with_text_3QLeqp","main"]}